{"tid":804462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 虐兒致危殆  被告求情時稱 工時長、壓力大","createTime":"2018-09-03T04:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T08:35:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"841829253ddb059d4fa2a551cab0079a5fe5d360","tid":804462,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:39:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名父親掌摑及搖晃初生女兒令女兒腦部嚴重缺氧，在高等法院承認襲擊等四項控罪，下午判刑。<br />\n<br />\n24歲被告鍾紀緣由囚車押送到高等法院應訊，他承認四項控罪，包括三項襲擊所看管兒童及一項刑事恐嚇罪。<br />\n<br />\n控方在庭上讀出案情，指被告前年12月在元朗家中，多次掌摑及左右大力搖晃約半個月大的初生女兒，女兒送院時腦部出血及嚴重缺氧。最新醫療報告顯示女嬰送院後一直危殆，要完全依賴呼吸機及餵食管道維生。<br />\n<br />\n被告代表律師求情時稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">被告任職廚師，工時長、壓力大</span>， 案發當日通宵工作回家，被女兒哭聲困擾，而女嬰母親及外婆並無理會，被告在沒有想過後果下猛力搖晃女兒，只是希望女兒不要哭，並沒有任何傷害她的意圖，希望法庭考慮被告沒有案底及認罪，女兒的情況令被告一世內疚已是很大的教訓，希望法庭輕判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=318908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318908&d=hzNM7YY%2BVeW%2BoBM08pddXzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3d2470bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318908&h=e67f6195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=318908</a>"},{"pid":"395faa0b4977890569fec6a6d7337d6b60bd1919","tid":804462,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"工時長、壓力大<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446f9b4841c8dbf8330c4775feeb233a68839dca","tid":804462,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"網絡打手都好大壓力"},{"pid":"526ba024ea24a40bfbf9ea09f6692258d5dcea9d","tid":804462,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime